<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 20:07:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在人质交易方面，保持权力始终是内塔尼亚胡最关心的问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/when-it-comes-to-hostage-deals-staying-in-power-is-always-netanyahus-paramount-concern/0000018d-7fbe-d636-adef-7ffeaf910000</link><description>从 1985 年开始，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在其政治生涯中参与了三起人质交易。他对与哈马斯潜在的新人质交易的立场仍然是个谜，但他肯定会研究民意调查，为自己找出最佳选择</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 19:50:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/when-it-comes-to-hostage-deals-staying-in-power-is-always-netanyahus-paramount-concern/0000018d-7fbe-d636-adef-7ffeaf910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列审查哈马斯对加沙停火、人质协议的反应；拜登：“似乎有点过头了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/israel-reviews-hamas-response-to-hostage-deal-biden-seems-a-little-over-the-top/0000018d-7f91-d6dc-ab9f-7ffd246e0000</link><description>在与最近一次访问中东的美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯会面后，卡塔尔总理补充说，哈马斯的反应“总体上是积极的”。他没有提供更多细节，但指出哈马斯对拟议交易有“评论”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 19:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/israel-reviews-hamas-response-to-hostage-deal-biden-seems-a-little-over-the-top/0000018d-7f91-d6dc-ab9f-7ffd246e0000</guid></item><item><title>第一批定居者，现在是网络：美国威胁取消间谍软件制造商的入境签证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/first-settlers-now-cyber-u-s-threatens-to-cancel-entry-visas-for-spyware-makers/0000018d-7f25-daa1-a9fd-7f2fd9640000</link><description>尽管美国长期以来一直寻求遏制间谍软件公司，并将 NSO 和 Intellexa 等公司列入黑名单，但以色列进攻性网络行业的消息人士表示，新政策是拜登和内塔尼亚胡之间紧张关系的一部分</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 19:30:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/first-settlers-now-cyber-u-s-threatens-to-cancel-entry-visas-for-spyware-makers/0000018d-7f25-daa1-a9fd-7f2fd9640000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯访问以色列：预计将讨论人质谈判、加沙计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/blinken-visits-israel-expected-to-discuss-hostages-gaza-war-and-day-after-plans/0000018d-7ee0-d636-adef-7eeecd300000</link><description>这是美国国务卿自10月7日以来第五次访问中东，美国和以色列正在考虑哈马斯对人质和停火协议的反应</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 18:08:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/blinken-visits-israel-expected-to-discuss-hostages-gaza-war-and-day-after-plans/0000018d-7ee0-d636-adef-7eeecd300000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 123 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-123/0000018d-7f91-daa1-a9fd-7f9b7eba0000</link><description>据以色列国防军、《纽约时报》报道，加沙剩余人质中至少有 32 名人质死亡 ■ 哈马斯对人质释放/停火协议作出“积极”回应 ■ 据报道，以色列向美国和联合国施压，要求允许近东救济工程处继续向加沙提供援助 ■ 绝大多数的以色列人认为下一次选举应该更早举行 ■ 战争结束 123 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:57:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-123/0000018d-7f91-daa1-a9fd-7f9b7eba0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 123 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-123/0000018d-7f86-d636-adef-7fee8ff00000</link><description>据《纽约时报》报道，根据以色列国防军的评估，加沙剩余人质中至少有 32 名人质死亡 ■ 哈马斯表示，它对拟议的人质释放/停火协议做出了“积极”回应 ■ 据报道，以色列正在向以色列施压美国和联合国允许近东救济工程处继续向加沙提供人道主义援助 ■ 绝大多数以色列人认为，下一次选举应该比指定日期 2026 年 11 月早得多举行 ■ 战争结束 123 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-123/0000018d-7f86-d636-adef-7fee8ff00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡抨击以色列国防军模拟以色列定居者绑架巴勒斯坦人的演习，要求调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-slams-idf-for-drill-simulating-settler-kidnapping-palestinian-demands-probe/0000018d-7f32-daa1-a9fd-7f3ad9e40000</link><description>以色列国防军发言人表示，此次演习是旨在提高西岸师战备状态的大规模演习的一部分。他补充说，“演练了 100 多种不同的场景，包括极端场景”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:40:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-slams-idf-for-drill-simulating-settler-kidnapping-palestinian-demands-probe/0000018d-7f32-daa1-a9fd-7f3ad9e40000</guid></item><item><title>“如果以色列不提供替代方案，加沙陷入混乱，我们最终将再次陷入哈马斯统治”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-02-06/ty-article-podcast/if-we-dont-offer-an-alternative-to-chaos-in-gaza-well-end-up-with-hamas-rule-again/0000018d-7eaa-d6dc-ab9f-7fff5ee50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:13:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-02-06/ty-article-podcast/if-we-dont-offer-an-alternative-to-chaos-in-gaza-well-end-up-with-hamas-rule-again/0000018d-7eaa-d6dc-ab9f-7fff5ee50000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列封锁资金，巴勒斯坦权力机构将减少公共部门工人的工资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/palestinian-authority-to-pay-reduced-salaries-as-israel-blocks-funds/0000018d-7f19-d6dc-ab9f-7f7d28fa0000</link><description>以色列财政部长指责拉马拉支持哈马斯，并拒绝释放以色列代表巴勒斯坦人征收的税收资金。巴勒斯坦权力机构表示，“将继续致力于保护囚犯和烈士以及加沙地带的人民”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:05:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/palestinian-authority-to-pay-reduced-salaries-as-israel-blocks-funds/0000018d-7f19-d6dc-ab9f-7f7d28fa0000</guid></item><item><title>这些年轻的特拉维夫艺术家正在面对 10 月 7 日和加沙战争的恐怖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/these-young-tel-aviv-artists-are-confronting-the-horrors-of-oct-7-and-the-gaza-war/0000018d-7e4b-d636-adef-7eef6f7d0000</link><description>五位来自不同领域的新兴艺术家饱受创伤和悲伤的折磨，正在努力应对哈马斯的袭击和随后的加沙战争。但正如其中一位所宣称的那样，“战后以色列艺术的一个历史时期将从这里出现”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 16:44:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/these-young-tel-aviv-artists-are-confronting-the-horrors-of-oct-7-and-the-gaza-war/0000018d-7e4b-d636-adef-7eef6f7d0000</guid></item><item><title>基督教影响者纳撒尼尔·布佐利奇 (Nathaniel Buzolic) 登陆以色列广告活动，被问及如何回归</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/christian-influencer-buzolic-lands-israeli-ad-campaign-is-asked-about-making-aliyah/0000018d-7eff-d636-adef-7efffe0d0000</link><description>前演员、现任亲以色列倡导者纳撒尼尔·布佐利奇 (Nathaniel Buzolic) 向一家以色列新闻媒体讲述了与当地模特莉亚·诺加 (Liya Noga) 约会、登陆他的第一个以色列广告活动以及为什么作为“非犹太文化”的人捍卫以色列是“强大的”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 16:05:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/christian-influencer-buzolic-lands-israeli-ad-campaign-is-asked-about-making-aliyah/0000018d-7eff-d636-adef-7efffe0d0000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查发现，大多数以色列人希望提前举行选举，约一半人反对加沙战争后建立巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/most-israelis-want-early-elections-about-half-oppose-palestinian-state-poll-finds/0000018d-7ec8-d636-adef-7eeec69a0000</link><description>以色列民主研究所的一项新民意调查显示，如果结束加沙战争的协议包括巴勒斯坦建国以及与其他阿拉伯国家达成和平协议，大约一半的以色列人会反对，只有 39% 的人认为以色列正在确保安全。其公民的</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 16:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/most-israelis-want-early-elections-about-half-oppose-palestinian-state-poll-finds/0000018d-7ec8-d636-adef-7eeec69a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队正在调查其士兵在加沙的数十起涉嫌违反国际法的行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-investigating-suspected-violations-of-international-law-in-gaza/0000018d-7e10-d25c-ad9f-fefc90c60000</link><description>在国际法院针对以色列的种族灭绝案中，以色列国防军正在审查加沙发生的事件，据报道，这些事件造成大量无辜平民死亡，以及对医院和学校的袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 14:42:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-investigating-suspected-violations-of-international-law-in-gaza/0000018d-7e10-d25c-ad9f-fefc90c60000</guid></item><item><title>“逆流而行”：极右翼阿根廷总统米莱开始访问以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/swimming-against-the-tide-far-right-argentine-president-milei-begins-israel-visit/0000018d-7de1-d008-a9cd-fff5ba0a0000</link><description>由于大多数拉丁美洲国家在加沙战争期间与以色列保持距离，阿根廷极右翼自由主义总统哈维尔·米莱开始对这个犹太国家进行首次正式访问。一位分析师表示，这看起来不像是阿根廷经过深思熟虑的战略，但它符合总统自己的信念。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 13:27:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/swimming-against-the-tide-far-right-argentine-president-milei-begins-israel-visit/0000018d-7de1-d008-a9cd-fff5ba0a0000</guid></item><item><title>“我没有死，但我不存在”：一个加沙家庭在欧洲白手起家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/im-not-dead-but-i-dont-exist-a-gazan-family-starting-over-in-europe/0000018d-7e21-daa1-a9fd-7e2bc2440000</link><description>瓦坦、拉菲克和奥萨马住在一家难民酒店，但仍在重温他们在加沙感受到和看到的破坏和痛苦，而加沙的未来和他们的未来都不明朗</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 12:35:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/im-not-dead-but-i-dont-exist-a-gazan-family-starting-over-in-europe/0000018d-7e21-daa1-a9fd-7e2bc2440000</guid></item><item><title>市政工作人员在以色列北部被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/municipal-worker-shot-dead-in-northern-israel/0000018d-7dda-d008-a9cd-ffff6f610000</link><description>阿德姆·哈穆德 (Adham Hamoud) 是西加利利地区委员会的一名工程师。警方表示，他们正在寻找枪手。哈穆德被杀是今年以来阿拉伯社会发生的第13起谋杀案</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 11:10:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/municipal-worker-shot-dead-in-northern-israel/0000018d-7dda-d008-a9cd-ffff6f610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队正在调查贝埃里基布兹房屋内 12 名人质的死亡事件，高级军官下令炮击房屋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-probing-death-of-12-hostages-in-beeri-house-shelled-on-orders-of-senior-officer/0000018d-7b6c-d008-a9cd-fbfdb0040000</link><description>总参谋部团队询问准将。 10 月 7 日下令开火的指挥官巴拉克·希拉姆 (Barak Hiram) 将军对事件的描述。以色列国防军原本计划等到战争结束后再调查该事件</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 05:40:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-probing-death-of-12-hostages-in-beeri-house-shelled-on-orders-of-senior-officer/0000018d-7b6c-d008-a9cd-fbfdb0040000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯并不急于达成人质协议。内塔尼亚胡政府也不是</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-is-in-no-hurry-to-seal-a-hostage-deal-neither-is-netanyahus-government/0000018d-7b29-d008-a9cd-fbfd41600000</link><description>上周的乐观情绪还为时过早 ■ 哈马斯领导层并没有放弃以色列从加沙全面撤军的要求，而内塔尼亚胡的强硬言论表明他无意同意 ■ 距离哈马斯的失败还有很长的路要走，这可能是拜登及其日后计划面临的问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 04:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-is-in-no-hurry-to-seal-a-hostage-deal-neither-is-netanyahus-government/0000018d-7b29-d008-a9cd-fbfd41600000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯表示，它已向卡塔尔和埃及做出了对停火、人质协议的回应；以色列军官在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article-live/netanyahu-gaza-war-will-take-months-not-years-un-to-investigate-unrwa/0000018d-7c7a-dcdb-a58d-fd7fcd7e0000</link><description>战时内阁成员甘茨：我们的目标是在没有以色列文职当局的情况下对加沙进行全面安全控制。 ■ 《纽约时报》报道：以色列正在评估加沙是否有至少 20 名人质被杀，以及 32 人确认死亡。 ■ 以色列国防军在约旦河西岸检查站射杀巴勒斯坦人；军队称，他们携带刀和枪 ■ 真主党称，他们用伊朗制造的 Falaq-1 重型导弹瞄准以色列北部 ■ 巴勒斯坦人在以色列北部基布兹开枪，房屋受损</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:43:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article-live/netanyahu-gaza-war-will-take-months-not-years-un-to-investigate-unrwa/0000018d-7c7a-dcdb-a58d-fd7fcd7e0000</guid></item><item><title>“对我来说是一个转折点”：加拿大主要自由主义犹太复国主义团体领导人辞职，称 10 月 7 日将他推向了右翼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/head-of-canadas-leading-liberal-zionist-group-quits-saying-oct-7-pushed-him-to-the-right/0000018d-7ba2-d008-a9cd-fbf793dd0000</link><description>乔·罗伯茨 (Joe Roberts) 发帖称，哈马斯的袭击动摇了他的政治信仰，以至于他不再认同 JSpace 的议程</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 00:03:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/head-of-canadas-leading-liberal-zionist-group-quits-saying-oct-7-pushed-him-to-the-right/0000018d-7ba2-d008-a9cd-fbf793dd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>